python 3.4.2
pybind11 git hash deb85f46efcba5fea624ee89daea8144abd77c54
gcc: arm-linux-gnueabihf-gcc ( 4.9.2-10) 4.9.2


It seems like bound functions are getting the same handling as normal functions, and thus do not properly capture "self". In pure python code this happens automatically, I do not know enough about the python C API to guess where this could be going wrong.

